WEBVTT

00:00:19.000 --> 00:00:19.460
Yumeng

00:00:20.980 --> 00:00:21.500
Yumeng

00:00:21.980 --> 00:00:22.620
Yuanqi

00:00:23.140 --> 00:00:23.519
I'm here.

00:00:24.199 --> 00:00:26.320
Yumeng, why did you come here?

00:00:27.219 --> 00:00:28.019
Yuanqi

00:00:28.780 --> 00:00:29.980
Seven Meridians Competition

00:00:31.039 --> 00:00:32.500
You must return safely.

00:00:33.320 --> 00:00:33.899
Promise me, okay?

00:00:36.759 --> 00:00:37.640
You don't need to worry about me.

00:00:38.119 --> 00:00:38.960
I'll be fine.

00:00:40.880 --> 00:00:42.600
How could I not worry about you?

00:00:43.119 --> 00:00:45.679
Father wants me to become the Jiang family's heir.

00:00:45.859 --> 00:00:47.340
He wants me to enter the secret realm trial.

00:00:47.579 --> 00:00:49.280
It's really just to stop me from going with you.

00:00:50.700 --> 00:00:51.859
Whenever I think about it,

00:00:52.579 --> 00:00:54.740
my heart is filled with

00:00:56.579 --> 00:00:57.659
all

00:00:59.079 --> 00:00:59.859
All what?

00:01:02.079 --> 00:01:03.859
It's all worry for you, silly.

00:01:04.340 --> 00:01:07.140
The Seven Meridians Competition isn't an ordinary contest.

00:01:07.780 --> 00:01:10.079
Win, and you'll be the leader of the righteous path.

00:01:10.980 --> 00:01:13.620
Power struggles have always been the cruelest.

00:01:15.140 --> 00:01:17.719
I didn't expect Father to use this to trouble you.

00:01:21.920 --> 00:01:24.200
Yumeng, it's fine.

00:01:24.939 --> 00:01:25.700
For you,

00:01:26.379 --> 00:01:27.560
I have to accept it.

00:01:53.980 --> 00:01:56.120
Yumeng, you...

00:01:56.120 --> 00:01:58.400
With my Ice Body, I took

00:01:58.400 --> 00:02:00.579
the Jiang clan's rare medicine,

00:02:00.700 --> 00:02:01.920
Hundred-Year Ice Crystal Essence.

00:02:02.079 --> 00:02:04.280
I condensed it into true energy and passed it to you.

00:02:06.319 --> 00:02:07.400
I hope

00:02:08.360 --> 00:02:12.020
it can accompany you through the competition in my place.

00:02:13.620 --> 00:02:14.319
Yumeng

00:02:18.280 --> 00:02:20.699
This quiet place is perfect for cultivation.

00:02:21.219 --> 00:02:22.280
I won't disturb you.

00:02:22.740 --> 00:02:23.539
I'll leave now.

00:02:37.139 --> 00:02:37.759
Yumeng

00:02:39.080 --> 00:02:39.780
Thank you.

00:02:41.080 --> 00:02:42.199
I will win.

00:02:56.639 --> 00:02:57.419
I believe in you.

00:03:05.740 --> 00:03:06.199
I'm leaving.

00:03:19.680 --> 00:03:20.979
Seven Meridians Competition

00:03:21.280 --> 00:03:22.819
officially begins.

00:03:30.719 --> 00:03:32.479
Plagues run rampant in the world.

00:03:32.740 --> 00:03:36.360
Cultivators must produce many pills each year to save people.

00:03:36.539 --> 00:03:38.099
The first trial of the Seven Meridians Competition

00:03:38.319 --> 00:03:40.199
is the medical trial: refining herbs.

00:03:40.900 --> 00:03:41.659
Eight fellow cultivators,

00:03:42.139 --> 00:03:43.919
in front of each of you

00:03:44.280 --> 00:03:45.500
is a hundred-herb altar

00:03:45.699 --> 00:03:46.800
and a Five Elements Furnace.

00:03:47.159 --> 00:03:49.199
Place Yuanling Grass into the furnace.

00:03:49.379 --> 00:03:51.500
Channel spiritual energy to form the pills.

00:03:52.180 --> 00:03:54.419
Whoever refines the most and best pills

00:03:54.840 --> 00:03:57.900
the top four may enter the next martial trial.

00:04:08.180 --> 00:04:09.219
How miserable.

00:04:09.400 --> 00:04:10.680
So overconfident.

00:04:12.060 --> 00:04:13.379
Looks like they can't withstand the poison.

00:04:20.879 --> 00:04:22.620
The Yuanling Grass in these altars

00:04:23.579 --> 00:04:24.319
is Duanhun Grass.

00:04:24.839 --> 00:04:25.439
That's right.

00:04:26.120 --> 00:04:28.339
The deadliest herb makes the best medicine.

00:04:28.720 --> 00:04:31.860
Medicine slaves only dare to dig it up with the soil.

00:04:31.959 --> 00:04:33.019
They don't dare touch it at all.

00:04:33.019 --> 00:04:35.600
I don't get these clueless commoner disciples.

00:04:35.600 --> 00:04:36.699
Why are they even competing?

00:04:36.740 --> 00:04:38.420
Right? Exactly.

00:04:38.420 --> 00:04:39.360
It's ridiculous.

00:04:41.259 --> 00:04:43.620
This tiny flame can't refine pills at all.

00:04:44.079 --> 00:04:46.199
Unless the cultivator has multiple elemental techniques,

00:04:46.779 --> 00:04:49.040
how can they refine pills with such a small flame?

00:04:56.360 --> 00:04:57.600
I'm poisoned.

00:04:59.579 --> 00:05:00.860
After all my effort,

00:05:00.899 --> 00:05:02.720
decades of hard cultivation,

00:05:03.279 --> 00:05:04.319
leaving my hometown,

00:05:04.680 --> 00:05:07.199
I finally climbed the 108-step heavenly ladder.

00:05:07.519 --> 00:05:09.319
I'm about to achieve success and fame.

00:05:09.680 --> 00:05:11.180
But now I'll die of poison here.

00:05:11.519 --> 00:05:13.920
The elders in my hometown are still waiting for me.

00:05:14.139 --> 00:05:16.699
I... I've let you all down.

00:05:18.379 --> 00:05:20.100
I've let you down.

00:05:20.279 --> 00:05:20.959
I'll save you.

00:05:26.379 --> 00:05:27.740
These commoner disciples

00:05:27.920 --> 00:05:29.459
I don't know what they do all day.

00:05:29.459 --> 00:05:30.959
Still dreaming of a leap to success?

00:05:37.480 --> 00:05:38.279
Thank you, benefactor.

00:05:38.600 --> 00:05:39.680
Why did you save me?

00:05:39.740 --> 00:05:40.420
No need for that.

00:05:41.120 --> 00:05:42.100
We are both commoner disciples.

00:05:42.819 --> 00:05:43.920
These noble disciples

00:05:44.379 --> 00:05:45.779
all see us as mere servants.

00:05:46.680 --> 00:05:48.160
We should look out for each other.

00:05:49.379 --> 00:05:50.279
Don't die here.

00:05:50.740 --> 00:05:52.339
Your people are still waiting for you to return home.

00:05:53.000 --> 00:05:53.600
Alright.

00:05:55.360 --> 00:05:57.120
Will Yuanqi be in danger?

00:05:57.660 --> 00:05:58.920
I'm really worried about him.

00:05:59.300 --> 00:06:00.740
What if something happens to him?

00:06:02.279 --> 00:06:03.379
He'll be fine.

00:06:07.839 --> 00:06:09.860
Another commoner disciple has started refining medicine.

00:06:09.939 --> 00:06:11.699
I bet he'll fail soon.

00:06:12.339 --> 00:06:14.740
This must be his first time seeing Duanchang Grass.

00:06:27.180 --> 00:06:28.319
Our clan leader has succeeded.

00:06:28.339 --> 00:06:30.120
Good, good, good.

00:06:30.879 --> 00:06:32.180
Our clan leader refined one too.

00:06:41.439 --> 00:06:43.639
This kid is interesting.

00:06:43.759 --> 00:06:45.600
But he's still far behind.

00:06:58.379 --> 00:07:00.160
He actually has three elemental attributes.

00:07:00.300 --> 00:07:03.540
Is this the legendary Sanhua Juding?

00:07:03.819 --> 00:07:04.600
That's impossible.

00:07:04.899 --> 00:07:07.360
Even noble clans rarely see this.

00:07:07.360 --> 00:07:08.860
A one-in-ten-thousand talent.

00:07:15.699 --> 00:07:18.220
He must have used some evil trick in this competition.

00:07:18.560 --> 00:07:19.759
This can't be real.

00:07:20.920 --> 00:07:23.519
A lowly commoner produced someone like this?

00:07:23.980 --> 00:07:25.879
Chen Yuanqi is remarkable.

00:07:26.040 --> 00:07:26.920
I didn't expect this.

00:07:27.759 --> 00:07:29.000
You've got some skills.

00:07:29.459 --> 00:07:30.939
I've got plenty more.

00:07:31.920 --> 00:07:33.420
Then be my son.

00:07:33.740 --> 00:07:34.980
Are you out of your mind,

00:07:35.399 --> 00:07:36.699
or did I hear you wrong?

00:07:36.699 --> 00:07:37.899
My mind is perfectly fine.

00:07:37.899 --> 00:07:39.040
And you heard me right.

00:07:39.379 --> 00:07:40.680
I admire you.

00:07:41.040 --> 00:07:43.660
Too bad I don't have a daughter.

00:07:43.839 --> 00:07:45.899
Otherwise, I'd marry her to you.

00:07:48.040 --> 00:07:49.560
I won't betray my family.

00:07:49.560 --> 00:07:49.980
You—

00:07:52.240 --> 00:07:53.740
I'll ask you one last time.

00:07:54.540 --> 00:07:56.000
Will you join the Fu family?

00:07:56.480 --> 00:07:58.160
I'll tell you one last time.

00:07:58.439 --> 00:07:59.199
Keep dreaming.

00:08:00.540 --> 00:08:01.139
Fine.

00:08:01.620 --> 00:08:02.259
Boy,

00:08:02.879 --> 00:08:04.920
you will die today.

00:08:13.699 --> 00:08:15.120
After I win,

00:08:15.480 --> 00:08:19.980
I'll make life even harder for all commoner disciples.

00:08:20.819 --> 00:08:22.800
They'll never rise up.

00:08:23.100 --> 00:08:26.199
So no one like you ever appears again.

00:08:33.779 --> 00:08:35.759
A divine pill refined with five elemental skills—

00:08:36.639 --> 00:08:39.679
Is this the legendary Wuqi Chaoyuan?

00:08:41.120 --> 00:08:42.559
Chen Yuanqi is in danger.

00:08:42.980 --> 00:08:45.399
Fu Cangtian will kill him after the battle.

00:08:46.059 --> 00:08:48.259
Sister Lie, what is Wuqi Chaoyuan?

00:08:48.779 --> 00:08:50.960
Wuqi Chaoyuan is a one-in-ten-thousand cultivation talent.

00:08:51.720 --> 00:08:53.519
It allows you to train five different skills at once.

00:08:53.679 --> 00:08:55.620
Cultivation speed is several times faster than normal.

00:08:56.879 --> 00:08:57.980
Then Yuanqi—

00:09:01.039 --> 00:09:02.240
This Chen Yuanqi kid—

00:09:02.340 --> 00:09:03.639
How can he compete with our clan leader?

00:09:03.840 --> 00:09:04.320
Exactly.

00:09:04.480 --> 00:09:05.740
What gives him the right?

00:09:05.919 --> 00:09:06.980
He's definitely not as good as our clan leader.

00:09:19.720 --> 00:09:20.919
Are we commoner disciples

00:09:21.019 --> 00:09:22.539
never going to have a chance to rise?

00:09:23.000 --> 00:09:26.100
Yuanqi, don't push yourself or you'll die.